            <h3>Directions</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Combine romaine, cucumber, tomatoes, olives, bell peppers, and red onion in a large bowl; sprinkle
                    with feta cheese.</li>
                <li>Whisk olive oil, lemon juice, oregano, and black pepper together in a small bowl. Pour dressing over
                    salad, toss well to combine, and serve.</li>
